sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Web Frontend
    participant API as SessionController
    participant S as SessionApplicationService
    participant R as Redis
    participant A as Audit Platform

    U->>FE: click Logout
    FE->>API: DELETE /auth/session/current
    API->>S: logoutCurrent(sessionId)
    S->>R: atomically delete session and remove from user index
    alt session already absent
        R-->>S: no-op
    else session revoked
        R-->>S: revoked
    end
    S->>A: logout.current.session
    S-->>API: success
    API-->>FE: clear client tokens
    FE-->>U: redirect to login
